160
00:12:39,364 --> 00:12:40,447
Wait for a while.

161
00:12:41,585 --> 00:12:43,510
Jap, go to the other side.

162
00:12:43,590 --> 00:12:44,697
Why are you hitting me?

163
00:12:44,777 --> 00:12:46,132
Take another route.

164
00:12:46,212 --> 00:12:48,068
I was hiding and got spotted.

165
00:12:48,148 --> 00:12:49,435
I escaped.

166
00:12:52,977 --> 00:12:54,233
Hurry, run.

167
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:56,369
Jap, your left.

168
00:12:58,890 --> 00:13:00,677
Come out, don't get killed.

169
00:13:02,008 --> 00:13:05,305
Jap, I think I heard footsteps just now.

170
00:13:05,385 --> 00:13:07,006
Something's wrong with your ears.
Don't disturb me.

171
00:13:07,086 --> 00:13:08,421
I'm trying to focus.

172
00:13:08,939 --> 00:13:10,046
Maybe it's Nubsib.

173
00:13:10,126 --> 00:13:11,423
