176
00:13:13,794 --> 00:13:16,489
Besides, he is too young.
He can't play with us.

177
00:13:16,569 --> 00:13:17,739
We are not kids.

178
00:13:17,819 --> 00:13:20,088
Do you think we should play
a childish game like hide-and-seek?

179
00:13:20,168 --> 00:13:21,513
Darn. Jap, run.

180
00:13:21,593 --> 00:13:22,736
