When will we reach there?

284
00:25:30,028 --> 00:25:31,498
Dear, you didn't forget anything, right?

285
00:25:31,578 --> 00:25:33,193
No. It's all here.

286
00:25:33,273 --> 00:25:34,287
Let's go.

287
00:25:37,751 --> 00:25:38,808
Get ready, kids.

288
00:25:47,447 --> 00:25:49,345
Are you ready, Gene? Jap?

289
00:25:49,709 --> 00:25:50,722
We're leaving.

290
00:26:44,150 --> 00:26:46,700
(Nubsib 31 Missed Calls)

291
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:59,400
This bottle is yours.

292
00:28:02,775 --> 00:28:05,757
But it's fine, you can take both,

293
00:28:06,224 --> 00:28:10,587
because my bottle
has been yours ever since you drank it.

294
00:28:26,206 --> 00:28:28,066
What's going on with all the barking?

295
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,318
Where did you come from?

296
00:28:42,231 --> 00:28:43,461
Where are you from?

297
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,150
Mr Gene.

298
00:29:18,171 --> 00:29:19,299
I miss you.

299
00:29:38,625 --> 00:29:40,046
How did you find this place?

300
00:29:40,545 --> 00:29:42,228
Aunty Run told me.

301
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:45,818
Are you still angry at me?

302
00:29:47,124 --> 00:29:48,225
Mr Gene.

303
00:29:48,306 --> 00:29:49,783
I don't want to talk to you.

304
00:29:49,863 --> 00:29:51,862
Can't you listen to my explanation?

305
00:29:51,942 --> 00:29:54,246
I don't want to talk to you.
I want to be alone.

306
00:29:54,326 --> 00:29:55,611
I like you.

307
00:30:05,725 --> 00:30:08,352
What a funny joke. Happy?

308
00:30:08,432 --> 00:30:09,952
You can go back if you're happy.

309
00:30:10,692 --> 00:30:11,994
I like you.

310
00:30:14,150 --> 00:30:16,645
-I hope you...
-Since the day you left me,

311
00:30:16,975 --> 00:30:21,363
you made me realize that I liked you.

312
00:30:22,961 --> 00:30:25,542
Is it that day
when you didn't even send me off?

313
00:30:26,105 --> 00:30:27,108
I...

314
00:30:27,188 --> 00:30:28,973
Enough. Not another word.

315
00:30:29,672 --> 00:30:32,917
That day,
I waited for you at the old place.

316
00:30:34,774 --> 00:30:36,938
The place where we first met.

317
00:30:40,727 --> 00:30:45,491
I hope you will change your mind
and look for me like you did in the past.

318
00:30:46,345 --> 00:30:47,644
I waited for a long time...

319
00:30:49,075 --> 00:30:50,365
but you didn't appear.

320
00:30:53,350 --> 00:30:54,536
Nubsib.

321
00:30:56,475 --> 00:30:57,817
Nubsib, where did you go?

322
00:30:57,897 --> 00:30:59,744
Why didn't you send Gene off?

323
00:31:03,481 --> 00:31:04,497
Nubsib.

324
00:31:04,577 --> 00:31:06,577
I'm asking you a question.
Why aren't you replying?

325
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:34,293
Gene.

326
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:16,068
I missed you.

327
00:32:18,417 --> 00:32:19,609
No.

328
00:32:21,315 --> 00:32:22,975
That's not all.

329
00:32:25,355 --> 00:32:27,045
I wanted you to come back.

330
00:32:36,508 --> 00:32:38,906
I want to be your only one.

331
00:32:40,171 --> 00:32:42,587
I want that you will only be hugged by me,

332
00:32:43,376 --> 00:32:47,734
only miss me and only love me.

333
00:32:52,950 --> 00:32:54,751
Do you believe what I say?

334
00:33:00,731 --> 00:33:02,187
About you liking me?

335
00:33:03,533 --> 00:33:04,631
Yes.

336
00:33:15,302 --> 00:33:16,778
Since then?

337
00:33:17,558 --> 00:33:19,114
Why are you still lying?

338
00:33:19,812 --> 00:33:21,495
You were so young at that time.

339
00:33:22,335 --> 00:33:24,118
How could you like anyone?

340
00:33:27,747 --> 00:33:29,351
I like you and that's the fact.

341
00:33:34,831 --> 00:33:36,691
I don't understand at that time,

342
00:33:37,194 --> 00:33:38,874
but I'm sure about it now.

343
00:33:40,318 --> 00:33:42,266
I told you back then, didn't I?

344
00:33:43,725 --> 00:33:45,475
If you still don't believe me,

345
00:33:46,437 --> 00:33:49,575
I have many ways to let you know that.

346
00:33:49,941 --> 00:33:51,033
No.

347
00:33:51,368 --> 00:33:52,581
There's no need.

348
00:33:53,950 --> 00:33:54,870
What is the reason...

349
00:33:54,950 --> 00:33:58,087
for lying to me about not having a place
to stay and not having a car then?

350
00:33:59,131 --> 00:34:01,057
Because I wanted to be together with you.

351
00:34:03,305 --> 00:34:06,878
If I didn't say that,
could I still live with you?

352
00:34:08,250 --> 00:34:11,739
If you've told me you are Aunty Orn's son,
I would even let you stay for a year.

353
00:34:11,819 --> 00:34:13,500
If I told you that,

354
00:34:13,975 --> 00:34:16,172
how would you treat me?

355
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:25,275
You should know.

356
00:34:26,275 --> 00:34:28,925
I don't want you to be my brother.

357
00:34:32,900 --> 00:34:35,234
I'm not forcing you to believe me.

358
00:34:38,625 --> 00:34:40,723
You can confess to me...

359
00:34:42,103 --> 00:34:43,966
when you believe me in the future.

360
00:35:02,165 --> 00:35:03,316
Fine.

361
00:35:04,700 --> 00:35:06,618
I want you to prove what you said then.

362
00:35:12,046 --> 00:35:15,805
I'm sure it would be romantic
if this is a novel.

363
00:35:16,854 --> 00:35:17,904
But now,

364
00:35:19,275 --> 00:35:20,572
you should know it, right?

365
00:35:20,911 --> 00:35:22,563
What you did was wrong.

366
00:35:25,114 --> 00:35:26,823
If you still lie to me,

367
00:35:27,496 --> 00:35:28,958
I'll definitely beat you up.

368
00:35:32,475 --> 00:35:35,354
I'm talking about your personality.

369
00:35:35,434 --> 00:35:37,344
Don't pretend to be a good kid.

370
00:35:37,424 --> 00:35:39,045
Just say whatever's on your mind.

371
00:35:40,074 --> 00:35:42,358
Like right now.
Say anything that comes to you.

372
00:35:46,950 --> 00:35:48,624
What does this expression mean?

373
00:35:54,725 --> 00:35:57,850
If you can't say it,
how am I going to believe you?

374
00:35:57,930 --> 00:35:59,512
Okay.

375
00:36:01,103 --> 00:36:02,345
I want to kiss you.

376
00:36:18,634 --> 00:36:19,851
I want you.

377
00:36:19,931 --> 00:36:21,118
Darn it!

378
00:36:21,198 --> 00:36:22,452
What are you talking about?

379
00:36:22,532 --> 00:36:25,138
You wanted me to say it, right?

380
00:36:25,684 --> 00:36:26,877
Well...

381
00:36:27,346 --> 00:36:29,439
You don't have to say everything out.

382
00:36:39,277 --> 00:36:40,267
Hey.

383
00:36:40,724 --> 00:36:42,159
Let me tell you something.

384
00:36:42,239 --> 00:36:44,745
I patted the dog's head just now.

385
00:36:45,226 --> 00:36:47,330
You are kissing the dog now.

386
00:36:54,411 --> 00:36:55,462
Then...

387
00:36:58,550 --> 00:36:59,905
Let's kiss the dog together.

388
00:37:36,350 --> 00:37:37,605
Taking advantage of me.

389
00:40:13,450 --> 00:40:14,385
Gene.

390
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:56,223
Do you know?

391
00:42:56,978 --> 00:42:58,467
Since you left,

392
00:43:00,357 --> 00:43:01,979
I've been very lonely.

393
00:43:05,050 --> 00:43:07,306
Now that we can be together again,

394
00:43:08,086 --> 00:43:09,902
don't disappear again.

395
00:43:46,850 --> 00:43:50,944
As the car started to move,
he kept looking at the rear-view mirror.

396
00:43:51,604 --> 00:43:55,478
But he didn't see the person
he wanted to see in the end.

397
00:43:56,141 --> 00:44:00,443
He felt sad like he had lost something.

398
00:44:01,355 --> 00:44:04,612
That separation is still memorable
in his mind.

399
00:44:05,164 --> 00:44:06,443
But now,

400
00:44:06,523 --> 00:44:09,434
the time they spent in the past
has resurfaced again.

401
00:44:09,514 --> 00:44:12,600
As for the memories that are fading,

402
00:44:13,041 --> 00:44:14,832
they become clear again.

403
00:44:14,912 --> 00:44:19,952
They meet again
and relit their affection for each other.

404
00:44:21,044 --> 00:44:23,903
Although the way
they meet again isn't considered joyful,

405
00:44:23,994 --> 00:44:26,187
it made him realize...

406
00:44:26,802 --> 00:44:29,767
the part that he lost
for quite some time in the past...

407
00:44:30,456 --> 00:44:32,646
has come back to hold him again.

408
00:45:06,390 --> 00:45:07,695
But you know it, right?
(On Next Episode)

409
00:45:07,775 --> 00:45:09,516
What you did was wrong.

410
00:45:09,596 --> 00:45:13,176
So,
I'll give us another chance to start over.

411
00:45:13,256 --> 00:45:16,207
But I won't allow you
to stay in my apartment.

412
00:45:16,287 --> 00:45:17,903
We can't stay together?

413
00:45:17,983 --> 00:45:19,359
Darn, that's enough.

414
00:45:19,439 --> 00:45:22,039
Hello.

415
00:45:22,119 --> 00:45:25,271
Nubsib, can you take a picture with Aey?

416
00:45:25,351 --> 00:45:26,397
Can you wait for a while?

417
00:45:26,478 --> 00:45:29,110
We are taking a photo
of Gene and Nubsib together.

418
00:45:29,190 --> 00:45:30,777
-You like Nubsib.
-If I...

419
00:45:30,857 --> 00:45:34,033
You knew I like Nubsib
but you still like him too.

420
00:45:34,113 --> 00:45:35,500
You're so bad, Gene.
